room_title: Escape room "The Hideout" by Lost Key Escape Rooms in Williston
room_description: As a young man, Valley-native Jerrie Otto wanted to serve his countryâ€¦ But being denied enlistment into every military branch (due to failing all mental health screenings) warped his glowing patriotism and drove Jerrie to build his own underground war-room.
